<p>Looking to do something new? Apply today for a Council education scholarship.</p>

<p>Whether you're wanting to study engineering at Colonia Applied Research, xenobiology at Balakor's Research Post, sociology at the Tir Research Labs, astrocartography at Hipparque, or any of the many other courses on offer, and whether you're needing an introduction to the basics or an advanced postgraduate qualification, with a Council scholarship your fees and reasonable expenses will be covered.</p>

<p>Colonia depends on all its people doing better than previous settlements have done, technologically, socially, ethically and scientifically. Pick up the application form from any system authority office today!</p>
